headlines.description: Australia's record-breaking run in World Cup qualifying ended on Tuesday when Aziz Behich's late own goal handed Japan the win.
headlines.shortLinkText: Late own goal earns Japan win, ends Aus. record

headlines.description: Alireza Jahanbakhsh's late header cancelled out Son Heung-Min's opener as Iran drew 1-1 with South Korea in Tehran on Tuesday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Iran's Jahanbakhsh heads home to cancel out Son strike
